ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n膠天使<br />\n年齡:????   生日:????   屬性:光<br />\n<br />\n身高:77CM   體重:9.2KG   血型:????型<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥系統:魔法<br />\n<br />\n高登公關的朋友,光體型宇宙人,會超能力,自稱絕對不會輸。<br />\n<br />\n　<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/25/4Zdpvk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2F4Zdpvk.jpg&h=6fe4aae0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n硬膠膠<br />\n年齡:10E1000  生日:10月10日   屬性:光<br />\n<br />\n身高:100CM   體重:77KG   血型:A型<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥系統:重力<br />\n<br />\n公正之神。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/07/Zl9ah4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2FZl9ah4.jpg&h=33d3cf85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n克洛洛斯<br />\n年齡:不明   生日:不明  屬性:光,金<br />\n<br />\n身高:181CM   體重:65KG   血型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />型<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥系統:不明<br />\n<br />\n時間之神,神話中是三神器主人的父親。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/08/i4wC3r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2Fi4wC3r.jpg&h=37fc54ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n獲黃<br />\n年齡:不明   生日:不明   屬性:光<br />\n<br />\n身高:192CM   體重:95KG   血型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />型<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥系統:武術<br />\n<br />\n獲黃的同伴,豹人族,死過一次,可變成超級傻豹。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/08/KG3i1o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F08%2FKG3i1o.jpg&h=40ac0c7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太監兔<br />\n年齡:不明  生日:不明   屬性:水<br />\n<br />\n身高:82CM   體重:28KG   血型:?<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥系統:魔法<br />\n<br />\n實力普通,有冶療能力,小時候不知什麼原因而去勢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/05/07/WUspV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F05%2F07%2FWUspV1.jpg&h=afe71df7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n絕望寶<br />\n年齡:????   生日:????   屬性:光<br />\n<br />\n身高:173CM   體重:60KG   血型:????型<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥系統:舞刃<br />\n<br />\n非洲力加朋友,認真狀態提升防禦,仙人狀態提升精神。<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/04/25/iaP8o0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F04%2F25%2FiaP8o0.jpg&h=59080b95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高登公關<br />\n年齡:????   生日:????   屬性:木,水<br />\n<br />\n身高:205CM   體重:135KG   血型:????型<br />\n<br />\n戰鬥系統:槍捧<br />\n<br />\n絕望寶的朋友,人馬型宇宙人,富正義感,不願跟病毒同流同污。"},{"pid":"c20a093996f41ea33ada348ad40e074be9922a53","tid":658164,"uid":46717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T03:28:46.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"206660da373f4039a021c3d77a08f9d53373061e","tid":658164,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T05:11:55.000Z","msg":"我啲流量阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fdee53fcf268ffb5edea2cd1593e4a73d2184c2","tid":658164,"uid":46717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"206660da373f4039a021c3d77a08f9d53373061e","tid":658164,"uid":32699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T05:11:55.000Z","msg":"我啲流量阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60235743de29c41dc852f68165e621c61d1d834","tid":658164,"uid":1971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"245ee1103aa613a1360f967b2e012fd2486a55df","tid":658164,"uid":3167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T17:38:31.000Z","msg":"有幾隻唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T03:18:15.000Z","msg":"有邊隻掂？"}]}